WEBVTT

00:15.510 --> 00:17.250
Spears are different
from swords or blades.

00:17.900 --> 00:19.200
The shaft is eight feet long.

00:19.750 --> 00:21.829
If you grip the end,
you won't have enough power.

00:21.830 --> 00:23.000
Hold it in the middle.

00:23.900 --> 00:25.040
Give it a try.

00:27.310 --> 00:29.250
Ever since Cangbei Gang entered
the city,

00:29.660 --> 00:32.290
Zhangru's been eager
to learn self-defense.

00:33.260 --> 00:36.389
But she only let Chen Jia teach her.

00:36.390 --> 00:38.010
I believe Chen Jia

00:38.500 --> 00:39.800
wouldn't harm Zhangru.

00:46.900 --> 00:48.040
Are you all right?

00:51.180 --> 00:52.109
Again.

00:52.110 --> 00:53.920
I have to teach you
how to properly handle it.

00:53.930 --> 00:54.890
Don't hurt yourself.

00:55.670 --> 00:56.810
There

00:57.980 --> 01:01.240
are three basic moves,

01:01.750 --> 01:03.109
block, grab, and thrust.

01:03.110 --> 01:04.840
Since you trust Chen Jia so much,

01:04.870 --> 01:07.200
why don't we make a bet?

01:07.340 --> 01:09.080
Let's see who's better
at judging people.

01:09.140 --> 01:11.720
How about six months?

01:12.030 --> 01:14.139
We'll see if you can win.

01:14.140 --> 01:15.280
Deal.

01:15.510 --> 01:16.720
Hold it in the middle.

01:17.950 --> 01:19.090
Further back.

01:20.030 --> 01:21.200
Lower your wrist.

01:22.750 --> 01:26.080
Block, grab, thrust.

01:33.180 --> 01:36.250
Block, grab, thrust.

01:38.590 --> 01:40.360
You're the slowest learner
I've ever taught.

01:45.980 --> 01:49.050
So, how many clever young ladies
have you taught before?

01:49.670 --> 01:51.410
I've never taught
any young ladies before.

01:51.830 --> 01:53.419
This move is called threshing wheat!

01:53.420 --> 01:54.810
That one's for cutting pig feed!

01:56.230 --> 01:58.080
And this is hanging laundry!

01:59.550 --> 02:00.699
These moves aren't half bad.

02:00.700 --> 02:01.599
So?

02:01.600 --> 02:02.589
I have plenty of moves.

02:02.590 --> 02:04.229
Who else have you taught?

02:04.230 --> 02:05.720
- No one!
- Who are they?

02:06.580 --> 02:07.720
Tell me!

03:26.610 --> 03:30.929
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

03:30.930 --> 03:34.190
=Episode 26=

03:36.730 --> 03:39.910
(Baifu Restaurant)

03:51.860 --> 03:53.000
Miss Miao.

03:56.790 --> 03:58.090
Song Han?

03:58.950 --> 04:00.210
What a coincidence.

04:02.580 --> 04:03.880
Wipe your sweat.

04:07.740 --> 04:11.000
You've given me a handkerchief
for the second time now.

04:14.350 --> 04:16.720
Why are you still here this late?

04:20.430 --> 04:21.779
Is this your shop?

04:21.780 --> 04:22.829
Yes.

04:22.830 --> 04:24.880
I'm about to check my nursery.

04:25.310 --> 04:28.290
Would you like to join me?

04:31.510 --> 04:32.730
Follow me.

04:40.260 --> 04:41.400
Here we are.

04:47.430 --> 04:48.570
Did you grow

04:49.260 --> 04:50.520
all these yourself?

04:50.580 --> 04:51.629
Yes.

04:51.630 --> 04:54.400
I planted some new crops
under the night dew.

04:55.020 --> 04:56.160
Ah, yes.

04:58.580 --> 05:00.259
This one here is a bean from the West.

05:00.260 --> 05:01.640
It flowers on the ground,

05:01.700 --> 05:03.949
and after the petals fall,
the branches dip into the soil

05:03.950 --> 05:05.290
and bear fruit.

05:05.390 --> 05:07.930
When you eat it,
it leaves a pleasant aftertaste.

05:08.700 --> 05:10.880
I've heard of it.

05:11.200 --> 05:15.200
In the south, it's called groundnut
because the flowers fall to the ground.

05:15.550 --> 05:17.760
You've been to the South?

05:18.660 --> 05:21.490
There was a music teacher I once knew

05:21.750 --> 05:23.490
who was from the coastal south.

05:23.900 --> 05:25.880
But he's no longer around.

05:29.990 --> 05:32.290
I'll give you

05:33.260 --> 05:34.400
my first batch of peanuts.

05:35.400 --> 05:36.259
I…

05:36.260 --> 05:37.930
Just like these peanuts,

05:38.260 --> 05:39.749
they will eventually bloom

05:39.750 --> 05:41.200
and bear fruit

05:41.750 --> 05:43.760
even though they grow in the dark.

05:52.100 --> 05:53.240
Thank you.

06:01.260 --> 06:02.259
My dear,

06:02.260 --> 06:03.400
time to eat.

06:03.950 --> 06:04.829
You go ahead.

06:04.830 --> 06:06.370
I still need to balance the ledger.

06:24.020 --> 06:25.440
Did you cook all these?

06:30.460 --> 06:32.560
Why did you cook so many dishes?

06:32.890 --> 06:34.899
You've worked hard these days.

06:34.900 --> 06:36.200
So this is a treat for you.

06:37.070 --> 06:39.099
I can't eat all of this by myself.

06:39.100 --> 06:40.429
Wouldn't it be a waste?

06:40.430 --> 06:42.960
If you enjoy it, it's not a waste.

06:43.900 --> 06:45.370
If you can't eat much,

06:45.550 --> 06:47.640
I can make smaller portions next time.

06:47.780 --> 06:49.429
Even a bite from each dish is fine.

06:49.430 --> 06:51.069
I can make plenty of different dishes.

06:51.070 --> 06:53.200
I want you to try them all.

06:54.340 --> 06:55.560
What's the rush?

06:55.660 --> 06:57.000
We have all the time in the world.

06:57.030 --> 06:58.690
I can try them slowly.

07:07.100 --> 07:08.240
What's wrong?

07:11.190 --> 07:12.330
Nothing.

07:13.260 --> 07:14.400
By the way, look at these.

07:25.410 --> 07:27.329
Several shops in the capital.

07:27.330 --> 07:28.910
Across thirteen provinces,

07:29.490 --> 07:32.350
there are iron mines in the north,
kilns in the south,

07:32.530 --> 07:35.790
salt fields in the west,
and tea plantations in the east.

07:36.010 --> 07:37.809
There are several ships

07:37.810 --> 07:39.350
in remote places like Penghu.

07:42.050 --> 07:43.550
I didn't know you were this rich.

07:45.410 --> 07:46.550
Did you think

07:46.690 --> 07:47.609
you married

07:47.610 --> 07:49.390
an impractical poor husband?

07:50.250 --> 07:51.409
My grandfather and mother

07:51.410 --> 07:53.430
were worried
about me being away from home.

07:53.530 --> 07:54.749
So they set up

07:54.750 --> 07:56.190
these businesses for me.

07:57.450 --> 07:59.910
You live simply,

08:00.090 --> 08:01.630
don't spend much on drinks,

08:01.730 --> 08:04.230
and have just a few outfits.

08:04.610 --> 08:05.769
I grew up in the military

08:05.770 --> 08:07.190
and don't have extravagant habits.

08:07.450 --> 08:10.070
My shops have been idle.

08:10.170 --> 08:12.950
So it's better
if I transfer them to you.

08:13.250 --> 08:15.510
They are suitable
for the Zhaowen Bookstore's use.

08:16.130 --> 08:18.190
Transfer everything to me?

08:19.090 --> 08:20.369
I'll ask our head manager

08:20.370 --> 08:21.529
to help you run them.

08:21.530 --> 08:22.910
This way,

08:23.130 --> 08:24.609
you can be hands-off like me

08:24.610 --> 08:25.750
and not have to worry.

08:28.930 --> 08:30.070
Yantang,

08:30.890 --> 08:34.790
why are you suddenly transferring
all this property to me?

08:35.850 --> 08:37.630
Did anything happen?

08:39.890 --> 08:41.809
You're the lady of the house.

08:41.810 --> 08:43.689
You should be managing these.

08:43.690 --> 08:45.569
I've wanted to hand them over
for a while.

08:45.570 --> 08:48.190
Plus, I could use a break.

08:55.100 --> 08:57.769
If we had two or three kids

08:57.770 --> 08:59.110
around with us,

08:59.170 --> 09:00.430
it'd be even better.

09:03.050 --> 09:04.190
I agree...

09:04.850 --> 09:06.590
How about we have a daughter?

09:08.450 --> 09:09.590
Sure.

09:10.290 --> 09:11.470
As long as you're happy.

10:04.090 --> 10:06.710
His Lordship wants us to stay
in the residence.

10:06.970 --> 10:08.830
So don't cause any trouble.

10:09.490 --> 10:10.630
No way.

10:10.650 --> 10:12.430
Even if the Marshal tried
to persuade me,

10:12.600 --> 10:14.690
I'm telling Madam everything.

10:16.090 --> 10:17.049
All right, then.

10:17.050 --> 10:18.049
Go ahead.

10:18.050 --> 10:20.529
Also, decide if you prefer quarrying
in Liaodong

10:20.530 --> 10:21.739
or fishing in Futing.

10:21.740 --> 10:24.209
Do you have a place to go
after His Lordship kicks you out?

10:24.210 --> 10:25.350
Go.

10:25.850 --> 10:26.990
What should I do then?

10:28.470 --> 10:30.169
He either goes out alone

10:30.170 --> 10:31.590
or travels miles for a case.

10:32.070 --> 10:33.750
Are we just letting him run wild?

10:34.930 --> 10:36.430
With his current state,

10:36.690 --> 10:38.590
he might collapse outside one day

10:38.820 --> 10:40.660
- and won't be found.
- Stop talking nonsense.

10:40.670 --> 10:41.870
- Who can't be found?
- Who...

10:45.210 --> 10:46.350
- Madam.
- Madam.

10:46.890 --> 10:49.310
I've seen Official Lu's prescription

10:49.810 --> 10:51.430
and checked Yantang's pulse.

10:52.450 --> 10:54.070
His pulse is strange.

10:54.290 --> 10:56.270
It's hard to say what the problem is,

10:56.610 --> 10:57.950
but something's definitely wrong.

10:59.210 --> 11:00.830
Do you know what's going on?

11:02.810 --> 11:04.270
- I don't know.
- I don't know.

11:04.970 --> 11:06.049
Madam,

11:06.050 --> 11:08.409
since Official Lu said
it was nothing serious,

11:08.410 --> 11:09.710
then it should be fine.

11:10.090 --> 11:11.230
Isn't that so, Lu Ming?

11:11.610 --> 11:12.750
Yes.

11:19.050 --> 11:21.990
What's the surprise? Why so mysterious?

11:22.090 --> 11:24.190
We're almost there. Be careful.

11:24.610 --> 11:25.649
All right.

11:25.650 --> 11:26.969
(Diecui Pavilion)

11:26.970 --> 11:27.929
We're here.

11:27.930 --> 11:28.889
Can I open my eyes now?

11:28.890 --> 11:30.030
Yes.

11:40.930 --> 11:42.070
What's this?

11:42.090 --> 11:43.230
Have a seat.

11:49.730 --> 11:53.390
This is the "Life of Luo Shan"
we watched together when we first met.

11:56.090 --> 11:59.110
In the play, Xu Jizu loses his mother,
seeks revenge on his father,

11:59.570 --> 12:00.950
and is severed from his family.

12:01.970 --> 12:03.230
It is truly unfortunate.

12:03.930 --> 12:05.070
So

12:05.330 --> 12:07.310
I wrote a happy ending for him.

12:07.730 --> 12:08.870
How about you watch it?

12:11.570 --> 12:14.230
But this misfortune follows him
throughout his life,

12:14.570 --> 12:16.030
leaving his soul restless.

12:17.090 --> 12:19.750
The first half of the play
is a tragedy destined by fate.

12:20.130 --> 12:22.870
Can it really be undone?

12:23.810 --> 12:25.150
There's always a way.

12:27.170 --> 12:30.070
Go back to the past
and start all over again?

12:34.770 --> 12:37.790
Though the destruction
of his family can't be repaired,

12:38.370 --> 12:41.230
life isn't just about the first half,

12:41.650 --> 12:43.350
and a person doesn't have
only one family.

12:44.330 --> 12:46.889
That's why I added

12:46.890 --> 12:48.590
a loved one for Xu Jizu.

12:49.630 --> 12:51.310
They built a new home,

12:51.880 --> 12:54.669
a home that keeps

12:54.670 --> 12:55.950
all storms and suffering out.

12:56.490 --> 12:59.990
A home that's priceless and unbreakable.

13:03.370 --> 13:04.510
Yantang,

13:08.440 --> 13:11.150
let's create such a home
for each other too.

13:12.130 --> 13:15.790
Those who've experienced
hardship know better how to cherish it.

13:16.410 --> 13:17.990
Two broken souls can piece together

13:19.250 --> 13:21.510
a complete whole.

13:26.450 --> 13:28.750
Shall we begin the play,
my dear audience?

13:59.970 --> 14:01.110
What's going on?

14:01.250 --> 14:02.390
Ms. Longevity,

14:03.610 --> 14:04.910
you dream of a peaceful life,

14:05.850 --> 14:09.350
enjoying the simple pleasures.

14:10.490 --> 14:11.630
I once thought

14:14.890 --> 14:16.790
I could protect you and keep you safe.

14:20.250 --> 14:21.430
But now

14:24.810 --> 14:26.070
I can't.

14:27.570 --> 14:28.870
All I have left

14:29.730 --> 14:31.510
are battles and revenge.

14:31.970 --> 14:33.470
I've offended half the court,

14:34.170 --> 14:35.550
turning everything upside down.

14:38.170 --> 14:39.310
I know that.

14:40.370 --> 14:41.790
I'll stay with you

14:42.090 --> 14:43.670
through life and death with no regrets.

14:44.570 --> 14:47.470
This turmoil will end someday.

14:47.970 --> 14:49.870
When it's over,

14:50.130 --> 14:51.350
we'll find

14:52.010 --> 14:53.990
a quiet place

14:56.010 --> 14:57.430
and set up a school.

14:57.930 --> 15:00.590
I'll teach literature,
and you'll teach martial arts.

15:01.210 --> 15:04.190
In spring, we'll enjoy the flowers
and go boating.

15:05.250 --> 15:06.390
In autumn,

15:07.730 --> 15:09.270
you can hunt for extra food.

15:10.050 --> 15:11.409
Our children

15:11.410 --> 15:13.550
won't suffer as we did.

15:16.410 --> 15:20.270
We'll have a big family
and grow old together.

15:21.130 --> 15:22.270
Ms. Longevity,

15:23.250 --> 15:24.390
I know

15:25.410 --> 15:27.950
your biggest wish
is to live well in this life.

15:28.610 --> 15:29.910
So don't worry.

15:30.490 --> 15:32.670
I'll clear all obstacles for you.

15:34.930 --> 15:37.110
With or without me,

15:39.290 --> 15:40.910
you can have a good life.

15:42.930 --> 15:44.110
How can I live a good life

15:44.410 --> 15:46.390
without you?

15:49.450 --> 15:50.329
I'm not feeling well.

15:50.330 --> 15:51.470
I should go.

15:54.170 --> 15:56.070
Are you hiding something from me?

15:58.930 --> 16:00.590
I want you to tell me yourself.

16:12.170 --> 16:13.310
Ms. Longevity,

16:15.290 --> 16:16.750
just trust me.

16:19.450 --> 16:21.550
I can give you my life.

16:22.370 --> 16:24.590
But your life is still yours to live...

16:27.850 --> 16:29.670
As long as we're together,

16:30.970 --> 16:32.150
your life

16:33.050 --> 16:34.670
is mine too.

16:35.490 --> 16:37.110
Why make a distinction between us?

16:40.330 --> 16:41.470
Ms. Longevity,

16:43.850 --> 16:45.030
trust me.

17:22.490 --> 17:23.630
Has the play started?

17:24.610 --> 17:26.070
Don't tell me it's over.

17:31.330 --> 17:32.550
Zhao.

17:32.810 --> 17:33.950
Ms. Longevity?

18:02.210 --> 18:03.590
Good lad,

18:03.650 --> 18:05.670
it feels powerful
even with a wooden blade.

18:05.970 --> 18:08.070
Next year, use a real one.

18:08.570 --> 18:11.550
But make sure to hold it steady

18:11.570 --> 18:12.710
and swing down.

18:13.690 --> 18:14.830
Keep practicing.

18:21.410 --> 18:22.550
Mo,

18:22.570 --> 18:25.670
I save you a piece
of peach blossom pastry.

18:57.530 --> 19:00.270
Hidden in the light,
admired for its ink.

19:00.770 --> 19:02.270
How about calling him Song Mo?

19:02.490 --> 19:03.630
That sounds great.

19:05.090 --> 19:06.230
Hey, Mo.

19:17.690 --> 19:25.070
("The Life of Luo Shan")

19:28.050 --> 19:29.609
(Exquisite Melodies)
- Good!

19:29.610 --> 19:30.689
The play is excellent.

19:30.690 --> 19:32.910
Too bad it is a tragedy.

19:33.130 --> 19:34.489
Well, not necessarily.

19:34.490 --> 19:37.070
People love to watch plays
because the plays always end up

19:37.130 --> 19:38.609
with a reunion

19:38.610 --> 19:40.190
no matter how deep the grudges.

19:40.940 --> 19:44.230
Life, on the other hand,
is harder than that.

19:52.080 --> 19:53.329
It's a drumstick.

19:53.330 --> 19:54.470
Correct!

19:54.490 --> 19:57.070
I'm surprised you know
about historical weapons.

19:57.530 --> 19:59.790
Could you be a man dressing as a woman?

20:00.220 --> 20:01.870
Well, women can be as capable as men.

20:02.890 --> 20:05.110
Allow me to be bold enough
to guess what's on your mind.

20:05.130 --> 20:06.910
I wonder if I am right.

20:09.210 --> 20:11.430
Allow me to be bold enough
to guess what's on your mind.

20:12.290 --> 20:13.590
I wonder if I am right.

20:19.490 --> 20:20.630
Three years...

20:26.890 --> 20:28.030
One year.

20:32.090 --> 20:33.350
After one year,

20:35.690 --> 20:37.190
my life will end.

20:40.410 --> 20:41.550
What was completed

20:42.570 --> 20:43.710
will be broken.

20:46.130 --> 20:47.950
I gained and then lost.

20:48.130 --> 20:50.870
Do you think hiding it
from me isn't breaking

20:51.130 --> 20:52.590
or losing?

20:53.570 --> 20:54.710
If

20:55.690 --> 20:58.070
you only have a year left to live,

20:58.410 --> 21:00.550
let's spend this year fully
as a married couple.

21:04.250 --> 21:05.710
If you really die

21:06.530 --> 21:08.030
in a year,

21:09.690 --> 21:13.390
my heart will still break

21:14.930 --> 21:17.190
whether we're together or apart now.

21:18.650 --> 21:20.550
So I can't let go.

21:20.930 --> 21:22.830
Every moment of this year,

21:23.010 --> 21:26.350
let's live a day like it's a year.

21:27.370 --> 21:28.510
A year

21:29.650 --> 21:31.310
will be our lifetime.

21:32.490 --> 21:34.710
I won't let my husband

21:35.770 --> 21:37.790
face life and death

21:39.170 --> 21:40.990
all by himself.

21:44.680 --> 21:49.189
♪You are the light
that saves me in the darkness♪

21:49.190 --> 21:52.959
♪Having you is a blessing♪

21:52.960 --> 21:56.439
♪Only by being by your side♪

21:56.440 --> 22:01.170
♪I can spend the rest of my life♪

22:02.290 --> 22:04.070
I was haunted by nightmares.

22:04.330 --> 22:07.430
There was always a woman
with a lantern who guided me.

22:08.530 --> 22:11.550
I later realized that the woman was you.

22:14.570 --> 22:16.150
You're the one

22:16.530 --> 22:18.030
I'd risk my life to protect,

22:18.770 --> 22:20.190
always.

22:30.210 --> 22:31.529
(Rest in the Flow,
Clarity in the Stones)

22:31.530 --> 22:40.190
♪See the future♪

22:41.810 --> 22:43.070
The Star of Love

22:44.050 --> 22:45.630
still shines.

22:47.090 --> 22:49.110
We've been waiting
and why are you only here now?

22:49.120 --> 22:51.110
Didn't you say you want
to watch the play with us?

22:51.120 --> 22:52.470
The play is already half over.

22:55.450 --> 22:58.510
I used to call you all fools
at the manor.

22:59.610 --> 23:00.750
But it seems

23:02.130 --> 23:04.030
I'm the biggest fool here.

23:05.170 --> 23:06.310
You eat it.

23:06.370 --> 23:07.510
All right.

23:09.130 --> 23:10.910
Is friendship less

23:10.930 --> 23:12.990
than romantic love?

23:14.890 --> 23:16.089
What's wrong?

23:16.090 --> 23:17.870
I've never seen you like this.

23:17.970 --> 23:19.990
What love? What friendship?

23:25.290 --> 23:27.129
Do you have feelings for Ms. Longevity?

23:27.130 --> 23:28.270
Tell me more.

23:29.570 --> 23:31.089
I don't have time for that.

23:31.090 --> 23:32.809
The country

23:32.810 --> 23:34.310
and the people needs me.

23:39.730 --> 23:42.089
But if Mantis Song breaks

23:42.090 --> 23:43.910
Dou Zhao's heart in the future,

23:43.970 --> 23:45.950
I'll face any danger

23:46.210 --> 23:48.110
to take her away.

23:50.450 --> 23:51.670
This play is so boring.

23:51.930 --> 23:53.350
How can you even watch it?

23:58.250 --> 23:59.080
Strange as always.

23:59.090 --> 24:00.910
Just let him be.
Let's keep enjoying the play.

24:04.970 --> 24:09.070
(Imperial Prison)

24:27.290 --> 24:28.590
Greetings, Your Grace.

24:28.730 --> 24:31.830
The lord has sent me
to give you something.

24:52.050 --> 24:56.670
Duke of Qijing would do anything
to please his youngest son

24:57.010 --> 24:59.550
like an ox being led by the nose.

25:04.050 --> 25:05.729
Are you using this story

25:05.730 --> 25:07.169
to threaten me with Han?

25:07.170 --> 25:08.710
How dare you!

25:15.370 --> 25:16.790
Your Grace, calm down.

25:17.210 --> 25:19.990
Be careful not to hurt yourself.

25:20.970 --> 25:23.070
The lord wants you

25:23.530 --> 25:26.750
to keep your mouth shut forever.

25:48.890 --> 25:50.350
All right.

25:50.930 --> 25:52.790
I'll be the ox for you

25:54.210 --> 25:56.350
this one time.

25:56.650 --> 26:00.150
(Yizhi Hall)

26:02.730 --> 26:04.289
My Lord, Madam.

26:04.290 --> 26:05.169
We caught

26:05.170 --> 26:08.190
this girl sneaking
around the back door of Yizhi Hall.

26:08.530 --> 26:09.689
Have mercy, Your Lordship.

26:09.690 --> 26:10.990
I'm not a bad person.

26:11.690 --> 26:13.339
After Madam passed,

26:13.340 --> 26:15.180
the Duke of Ying let me go back
to my village.

26:15.250 --> 26:18.350
I came to ask for some travel money.

26:19.130 --> 26:20.270
Madam?

26:21.610 --> 26:23.110
You're Li Yaoniang's maidservant?

26:25.130 --> 26:26.990
If you were Li Yaoniang's maidservant,

26:27.410 --> 26:29.830
what were you doing when she died?

26:30.670 --> 26:33.700
That night,
the Second Young Master visited Madam.

26:33.850 --> 26:34.769
I was told to leave

26:34.770 --> 26:36.230
and wasn't in the courtyard.

26:37.170 --> 26:39.070
So I don't know what they talked about.

26:39.610 --> 26:40.950
The next morning,

26:41.370 --> 26:43.030
Madam Li hanged herself.

26:44.650 --> 26:45.790
Are you saying

26:46.730 --> 26:48.129
Song Han visited Li Yaoniang

26:48.130 --> 26:49.750
the night before she died?

26:59.690 --> 27:01.329
How can you not keep an eye on a cat?

27:01.330 --> 27:02.750
Where did it go?

27:03.250 --> 27:04.609
I've sent all the servants

27:04.610 --> 27:05.689
to look for it.

27:05.690 --> 27:06.830
Find it now!

27:07.130 --> 27:09.110
How am I supposed to eat
without that creature?

27:09.770 --> 27:10.910
Yes, Young Master.

27:11.770 --> 27:14.310
The maids at Xixiang Place said

27:15.250 --> 27:16.729
that Song Han has a habit

27:16.730 --> 27:18.750
of feeding the cat before every meal.

27:20.170 --> 27:21.630
It seems

27:22.570 --> 27:25.110
this is more than just feeding the cat.

27:28.850 --> 27:30.190
I'll take care of this.

27:31.210 --> 27:32.510
Don't interfere.

27:34.330 --> 27:36.270
Xingshuang, I told you...

27:42.170 --> 27:43.310
Mo.

27:44.410 --> 27:47.350
Your cat went to Yizhi Hall again.

27:50.730 --> 27:51.870
Yes,

27:52.520 --> 27:53.740
it's just mischievous.

27:54.410 --> 27:56.190
I heard you haven't eaten all day.

27:57.610 --> 27:59.470
Not many people would lose
their appetite

28:00.650 --> 28:02.230
over a cat.

28:04.530 --> 28:05.920
When you've kept it for a long time,

28:06.890 --> 28:08.460
you get attached.

28:08.490 --> 28:11.830
Also, I don't have much
of an appetite today.

28:12.810 --> 28:14.230
Do you have anything to tell me

28:15.930 --> 28:17.430
about my mother's death?

28:20.770 --> 28:21.910
Mo,

28:23.690 --> 28:24.830
what do you mean?

28:25.450 --> 28:26.630
I don't know anything.

28:32.730 --> 28:34.270
I'll give you one last chance.

28:36.370 --> 28:37.510
Do you?

28:40.810 --> 28:41.950
No.

28:45.650 --> 28:46.790
Mo!

28:47.290 --> 28:48.139
Mo!

28:48.140 --> 28:49.689
I really don't know anything.

28:49.690 --> 28:51.710
(Freedom from Worries)

28:56.090 --> 28:57.350
I'll ask you one more time.

28:58.690 --> 29:00.270
Do you have anything to tell me

29:00.770 --> 29:02.070
about my mother's death?

29:02.410 --> 29:03.689
I really don't know

29:03.690 --> 29:05.390
who poisoned Mother.

29:10.690 --> 29:12.150
I never said

29:12.650 --> 29:14.110
Mother was poisoned to death.

29:21.850 --> 29:23.270
I don't want to see a single lie

29:23.530 --> 29:25.590
in your testimony.

29:25.770 --> 29:27.510
This is your last chance

29:28.970 --> 29:31.350
and also the last time I see you.

29:43.970 --> 29:45.710
Mo, stop!

29:51.410 --> 29:52.550
Mo.

29:53.410 --> 29:54.870
If you don't believe me,

29:56.650 --> 29:58.430
I'll prove my innocence with my death.

30:02.380 --> 30:03.520
My Lord.

30:18.550 --> 30:19.569
Mo.

30:19.570 --> 30:21.630
Mo, it really has nothing to do with me.

30:22.290 --> 30:23.430
It was Father.

30:24.570 --> 30:27.390
Father asked me
to deliver medicine to Mother that day.

30:27.610 --> 30:30.030
I didn't suspect anything
and gave it to her.

30:30.730 --> 30:33.790
It was only after she died

30:34.150 --> 30:35.920
that I found out
the medicine I sent to her

30:36.570 --> 30:38.230
was poison.

30:39.890 --> 30:41.390
I was afraid Father would poison me.

30:41.930 --> 30:43.430
So I used the cat to test for poison.

30:43.970 --> 30:45.670
I didn't tell you

30:46.290 --> 30:48.710
because I was afraid our family

30:49.650 --> 30:51.230
would fall apart.

31:11.810 --> 31:13.289
Take him back.

31:13.290 --> 31:14.430
Yes, Your Lordship.

31:40.210 --> 31:41.390
Yantang!

31:45.730 --> 31:46.910
Yantang!

31:48.250 --> 31:49.430
Yantang!

31:51.570 --> 31:52.910
Your pulse is very erratic.

31:53.410 --> 31:55.790
I'm not sure if the poison
has affected your organs.

31:56.170 --> 31:58.150
I'll send for Official Lu.

32:01.490 --> 32:02.630
I'm all right.

32:02.810 --> 32:04.230
There's no need to make a fuss.

32:04.410 --> 32:06.870
It's only a rush of blood.

32:10.570 --> 32:11.710
By the way,

32:12.010 --> 32:13.919
I found some discrepancies

32:13.920 --> 32:15.990
in Xixiang Place's ledger.

32:16.370 --> 32:18.910
So I asked Mr. Chen to take my token

32:19.010 --> 32:20.950
and inquire at the shops we frequent.

32:21.890 --> 32:23.030
It turns out

32:24.170 --> 32:25.929
that during your mother's illness,

32:25.930 --> 32:28.510
the household purchased

32:28.730 --> 32:30.510
large quantities of licorice
several times.

32:31.930 --> 32:34.070
This matches our suspicion

32:34.650 --> 32:36.990
that Mother's illness
was caused by licorice.

32:38.290 --> 32:40.449
Qi Xia's current madness

32:40.450 --> 32:42.230
must be related to her death.

32:42.570 --> 32:44.070
Once Qi Xia regains her sanity,

32:44.250 --> 32:45.950
we'll know what happened.

32:50.330 --> 32:52.150
How do you plan to deal with Song Han?

32:55.970 --> 32:58.750
Maybe I've misunderstood him.

32:59.090 --> 33:01.230
He's just a frightened child.

33:11.930 --> 33:12.929
Father,

33:12.930 --> 33:14.550
how could you do such a thing?

33:15.610 --> 33:16.649
She's my mother.

33:16.650 --> 33:18.350
She's not your mother.

33:18.410 --> 33:19.259
With Shuyao,

33:19.260 --> 33:21.790
the three of us are a true family.

33:22.830 --> 33:24.289
If it weren't for them,

33:24.290 --> 33:26.150
I wouldn't be a child out of wedlock!

33:26.530 --> 33:27.950
I am my mother's son.

33:28.210 --> 33:29.729
I'm not Li Yaoniang's son!

33:29.730 --> 33:31.110
Li Yaoniang was not qualified!

33:31.530 --> 33:33.289
Han, but I am...

33:33.290 --> 33:34.630
Madam Li, please mind your words.

33:34.930 --> 33:37.090
You chose this path for me
as the Second Young Master

33:37.570 --> 33:39.010
of the Duke's household.

33:40.690 --> 33:42.310
Mother, it's time for your medicine.

33:42.480 --> 33:45.169
I could have been a dutiful
and honorable son

33:45.170 --> 33:46.310
and brother.

33:46.330 --> 33:48.609
But now I live

33:48.610 --> 33:50.220
in constant danger and unease.

33:53.770 --> 33:55.230
Mother, don't eat it.

33:55.250 --> 33:56.169
You can't eat it.

33:56.170 --> 33:57.670
I don't know anything.

33:59.010 --> 34:00.310
You doted on me the most.

34:01.020 --> 34:02.089
No matter what I did wrong,

34:02.090 --> 34:03.489
you would never blame me.

34:03.490 --> 34:05.550
It's the same this time,

34:06.010 --> 34:07.150
right?

34:10.090 --> 34:11.470
You're right, Second Young Master.

34:12.730 --> 34:14.350
I didn't consider it carefully enough.

34:19.010 --> 34:20.350
I wasn't born out of wedlock.

34:22.690 --> 34:24.190
I'm the Second Young Master

34:25.420 --> 34:26.750
of the Duke of Ying's household.

34:41.970 --> 34:42.849
Miss Miao,

34:42.850 --> 34:45.270
Second Young Master hasn't eaten
for days.

34:45.290 --> 34:47.590
He still throws the medicine
and drives people away.

34:47.970 --> 34:50.430
Miss Miao, maybe you should leave.

35:11.010 --> 35:12.150
Get out.

35:17.520 --> 35:19.110
This is a snowflake pastry.

35:23.010 --> 35:26.550
It's made
with top-quality flour, steamed,

35:26.570 --> 35:28.910
and soaked in butter.

35:29.010 --> 35:31.430
It's soft and sweet.

35:38.450 --> 35:39.870
This is pepper and salt cake.

35:40.330 --> 35:41.769
It's made with two jin of flour,

35:41.770 --> 35:43.310
half a jin of sesame oil,

35:43.410 --> 35:44.550
and two liang of salt.

35:44.890 --> 35:47.910
It's crispy and fragrant,

35:48.010 --> 35:50.510
spicy and delicious.

35:53.610 --> 35:54.910
This is taro pastry.

35:55.010 --> 35:57.529
It's made with raw taro
and glutinous rice flour.

35:57.530 --> 35:59.920
When it's filled with red bean paste,
it's absolutely heaven.

36:01.010 --> 36:02.310
If you don't like these,

36:02.330 --> 36:03.889
I have other varieties.

36:03.890 --> 36:07.110
I have chive cakes, white pastry cakes,
and sugar oil cakes.

36:07.250 --> 36:08.849
I'm sure there's something you'll like.

36:08.850 --> 36:09.990
Take a look.

36:21.010 --> 36:23.070
Eat slowly or you'll choke.

36:31.890 --> 36:33.510
This medicine is too bitter.

36:33.730 --> 36:35.190
I won't taste it for you.

36:49.010 --> 36:50.529
(Natural Grace and Talent)

36:50.530 --> 36:54.830
By the mandate of heaven,
His Majesty decrees

36:55.010 --> 36:57.669
that Song Mo has done well
in solving the case.

36:57.670 --> 36:59.449
His Majesty is pleased.

36:59.450 --> 37:02.009
(Song's Ancestral Hall)
Song Mo shall be promoted to Commander,

37:02.010 --> 37:04.289
granted the right
to enter the palace with a sword,

37:04.290 --> 37:06.270
and exempt from kneeling.

37:06.370 --> 37:08.230
(Peaceful Family, Thriving Life)
Thus decreed by the Emperor.

37:10.010 --> 37:11.670
Thank you, Your Majesty.

37:18.850 --> 37:21.769
The emperor has another decree.

37:21.770 --> 37:23.830
You can read it yourself, Your Lordship.

37:27.170 --> 37:28.670
Sir, come this way.

37:36.970 --> 37:38.110
What's the matter?

37:39.050 --> 37:40.470
Song Yichun submitted a memorial,

37:40.970 --> 37:43.310
confessing to abusing power
and harming the innocent.

37:44.170 --> 37:45.350
He died of illness

37:46.330 --> 37:47.710
in prison.

37:53.130 --> 37:56.830
(Memorial Tablet of Song Yichun)

38:05.170 --> 38:06.710
Han is still young.

38:07.170 --> 38:09.230
Losing both parents in a short time

38:09.810 --> 38:11.190
is truly hard to bear.

38:11.810 --> 38:13.190
Han isn't the only one

38:13.410 --> 38:14.990
to lose both parents.

38:18.010 --> 38:19.870
My last meeting with Song Yichun ended

38:20.610 --> 38:22.870
our father-son relationship.

38:23.570 --> 38:24.710
From now on,

38:26.090 --> 38:27.550
I only have a deceased mother,

38:27.970 --> 38:29.310
no deceased father.

38:30.290 --> 38:31.590
Once the funeral is over,

38:31.770 --> 38:33.590
this matter will be settled.

38:33.970 --> 38:36.870
What do you plan to do about Han?

38:37.650 --> 38:39.470
Song Yichun wronged my mother.

38:40.010 --> 38:42.350
Han is an innocent victim.

38:43.800 --> 38:46.110
Let him continue living
at Xixiang Place.

39:01.890 --> 39:03.510
Moments of happiness are short-lived.

39:04.950 --> 39:06.920
The days gone by are filled
with so much sorrow.

39:13.050 --> 39:16.550
(The past fades into mystery,
its wisdom lost.)

39:16.551 --> 39:20.350
(Yet the east wind stirs,
and rain brings a new dawn.)

39:25.170 --> 39:26.470
Han,

39:27.370 --> 39:30.750
I can't stay with you much longer.

39:31.530 --> 39:33.230
From now on,

39:33.850 --> 39:36.110
you must walk this path on your own.

39:37.290 --> 39:39.910
My advice to you

39:41.370 --> 39:42.950
is to stay away from the court

39:43.170 --> 39:46.870
and live a simple life.

39:47.330 --> 39:48.910
If being a commoner is so good,

39:49.650 --> 39:51.710
why did you insist on becoming a Duke?

39:53.250 --> 39:55.190
It's fine if you ruin your own life.

39:55.810 --> 39:58.310
But why take away my chance
to climb higher?

39:59.930 --> 40:01.070
I did it all

40:01.610 --> 40:03.470
for your best interests.

40:03.930 --> 40:05.470
How is this my best interests?

40:05.980 --> 40:08.209
If you hadn't insisted on revealing
my lineage,

40:08.210 --> 40:10.150
our family wouldn't have been destroyed.

40:11.490 --> 40:13.150
I ended up in this miserable state

40:13.260 --> 40:14.600
because of you!

40:14.810 --> 40:15.950
You...

40:19.370 --> 40:21.150
Father... Father.

40:21.170 --> 40:22.310
What's the matter, Father?

40:27.850 --> 40:29.270
- Father.
- My medicine.

40:29.650 --> 40:30.790
My medicine...

40:40.290 --> 40:42.249
(Memorial Tablet of Song Yichun)
(Father,)

40:42.250 --> 40:45.430
(you had average achievements
all your life,)

40:46.100 --> 40:47.750
(but you died with honor.)

40:48.770 --> 40:50.150
(I'll carry on)

40:51.250 --> 40:53.030
(your unfinished business.)

41:01.490 --> 41:04.150
(Song's Ancestral Hall)

41:05.050 --> 41:08.990
By the emperor's decree,

41:09.410 --> 41:12.270
former Duke Song Yichun
was stripped of his title

41:12.690 --> 41:14.710
(Meritorious Service)
for his crimes.

41:14.970 --> 41:17.030
His demise has cleared his offenses.

41:17.610 --> 41:21.870
His eldest son, Song Mo,
known for his virtue and loyalty,

41:22.250 --> 41:24.190
and assist the nation with propriety,

41:25.650 --> 41:28.230
shall inherit the title of Duke of Ying.

41:28.770 --> 41:33.109
His wife, Dou Zhao,
is conferred the title Duchess of Ying.

41:33.110 --> 41:35.550
Your Graces.

41:35.690 --> 41:38.110
Your Graces.

41:40.050 --> 41:41.190
Yantang,

41:41.530 --> 41:44.009
the whole household

41:44.010 --> 41:46.390
will be relying on you now.

41:47.770 --> 41:49.310
You're being overly courteous.

41:49.560 --> 41:51.389
We watched them grow up.

41:51.390 --> 41:52.910
How can they not be filial to us?

41:53.250 --> 41:54.390
First Aunt,

41:54.850 --> 41:57.870
I don't recall us being
this close before.

42:01.370 --> 42:02.510
Zhao,

42:02.530 --> 42:04.889
I made new clothes for you.

42:04.890 --> 42:06.310
See if you like them.

42:06.850 --> 42:08.030
The ceremony is over.

42:08.490 --> 42:10.550
The Duchess has other duties
to attend to.

42:10.730 --> 42:12.230
Excuse us.

42:18.970 --> 42:20.089
Third Aunt,

42:20.090 --> 42:22.670
I apologize on behalf of Sister-in-law.

42:22.770 --> 42:24.630
Brother has just been appointed Duke

42:24.730 --> 42:27.630
and surely has much to handle.

42:29.030 --> 42:30.329
Who does Dou Zhao think she is?

42:30.330 --> 42:31.590
Acting so high and mighty.

42:32.050 --> 42:33.729
Does she not know
how she became Duchess?

42:33.730 --> 42:34.889
It was because Song Mo forced

42:34.890 --> 42:36.710
his father to death in prison!

42:36.970 --> 42:38.910
Enough, you should stop talking.

42:39.610 --> 42:41.030
With this couple around,

42:41.490 --> 42:43.950
we will have a hard time from now on.

42:59.330 --> 43:00.689
If we don't get rid of Song Mo,

43:00.690 --> 43:01.730
he will always be a threat.

43:01.740 --> 43:03.690
If we can't make a move
against him on the court,

43:03.700 --> 43:04.969
we'll strike from his household.

43:04.970 --> 43:07.289
The Snow Ganoderma of Liaodong blooms
only once every 300 years.

43:07.290 --> 43:08.920
It can bring people back
from the brink of death.

43:08.930 --> 43:10.689
You are wise and astute.

43:10.690 --> 43:12.089
If you won't be my ally,

43:12.090 --> 43:14.049
you can only be an enemy.

43:14.050 --> 43:18.470
♪Can anyone ease the pain of goodbye?♪

43:18.770 --> 43:21.950
♪If dreams are shattered,
can they be whole again?♪

43:22.530 --> 43:26.110
♪If today brings hope, will it stay?♪

43:26.210 --> 43:32.110
♪Will the pain just weave
itself deeper?♪

43:32.250 --> 43:33.769
♪Where can this restless heart
find peace?♪

43:33.770 --> 43:36.849
♪Left alone in an empty hall♪

43:36.850 --> 43:40.710
♪A lifetime chasing fate's lonely call♪

43:40.770 --> 43:45.009
♪Watching seasons fade and storms rise♪

43:45.010 --> 43:47.569
♪It hurts but it's not all for nothing♪

43:47.570 --> 43:48.849
♪My heart is as empty as a quiet street♪

43:48.850 --> 43:51.889
♪Who cares about the path I walk alone?♪

43:51.890 --> 43:56.049
♪Would you take away
the weight of the past?♪

43:56.050 --> 43:58.049
♪Life is fleeting, like morning frost♪

43:58.050 --> 44:01.249
♪Even a moment feels endless with you♪

44:01.250 --> 44:07.390
♪Like a stream flowing steady
through time♪

44:09.370 --> 44:16.270
♪A lone flower falls from the eaves
Moonlight graces steps beneath♪

44:16.730 --> 44:23.950
♪Can anyone ease the pain of goodbye?♪

44:24.250 --> 44:27.470
♪If dreams are shattered,
can they be whole again?♪

44:28.050 --> 44:31.630
♪If today brings hope, will it stay?♪

44:31.730 --> 44:37.630
♪Will the pain just weave
itself deeper?♪

44:38.250 --> 44:39.529
♪In this chaotic world♪

44:39.530 --> 44:42.489
♪Only love lasts♪

44:42.490 --> 44:46.230
♪We'll get through
every challenge together♪

44:46.410 --> 44:50.649
♪No matter how cold
or uncertain the road♪

44:50.650 --> 44:53.249
♪There's nothing to fear
when I'm with you♪

44:53.250 --> 44:54.449
♪My heart feels empty♪

44:54.450 --> 44:57.369
♪But I can hear your voice♪

44:57.370 --> 45:01.649
♪In this life, under moonlight
and across the oceans♪

45:01.650 --> 45:04.070
♪We'll find our way back to each other♪

45:04.330 --> 45:05.169
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

45:05.170 --> 45:06.049
(Every medical behaviour involved
and medicine used in the drama)

45:06.050 --> 45:07.049
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home)

45:07.050 --> 45:13.150
♪Together,
we'll make every moment count♪
